high_descs: Turn around, go right across the room to the opposite side, and, before reaching a stove on the right, turn right to face a counter
Pick up an apple from the counter.
Put the apple in the microwave, heat it up for a while, and take it out.
Head back towards the place where you picked up the apple, but turn the opposite way from the counter and go to a fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place the heated-up apple in the fridge

high_descs: Turn back and walk, turn right and walk across the microwave, turn right and head to the counter top.
Pick up the apple left to the stove with vessel on it from the counter top.
Turn right, walk, and turn left, head to the microwave.
Put the apple into the microwave, heat it up, and pick it up back.
Turn left and walk, again turn left and walk, head to the fridge.
Put the apple in the last rack of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated apple inside the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and move towards the counter top
pick the apple from the counter top
open the oven,place the apple inside for some time and take it out and close the oven
place the cooked apple inside the fridge
anns.task_desc: place the cooked apple inside the fridge
